To build and install the PlusGraph library and application, run:

$ make
$ sudo make install

In order to build the PlusGraph application, you need the PlusCalc library, which can be found at https://github.com/jansky/PlusCalc

The installation process does the following:

cp plusgraph /usr/bin
cp libplusgraph.a /usr/lib
cp plusgraph.h /usr/include

To uninstall PlusGraph, run:

$ sudo make uninstall

To clean, run:

$ make clean